  "text": "The DeAngelo model has its limitations. Firstly, if nondiscretionary accruals vary across periods, the model will measure discretionary accruals with error. Secondly, the model does not take account of the impact of changes in economic circumstances on nondiscretionary accruals [CITATION_1] . Thirdly, as the power of the model is low, it may not detect all instances of earnings management [CITATION_2] ).",
